Serialized Form

  • Package com.mobilab.accountservice.bussiness.message

    • Class com.mobilab.accountservice.bussiness.message.MyRequest extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      7269757532294474877L

      • Serialized Fields

        • requestType

          short requestType
          should be one of the fields above to show the type of the request

        • id

          long id
          message id which is assigned by gate

        • gateID

          java.lang.Long gateID
          id of the gate process

        • sender

          java.lang.String sender
          end user id, IP or name

        • timestamp

          long timestamp
          time stamp of message when it arrives , assigned by gate

        • returnUpdated

          java.lang.Boolean returnUpdated
          if true then response includes updated account. in read requests is null.

        • typeUpdate

          java.lang.Short typeUpdate
          which parts should be updated in update requests, for example: TYPE_ONLY_BALANCE

        • typeReturned

          java.lang.Short typeReturned
          which parts should be returned in update and read requests, for example: TYPE_ONLY_BALANCE

        • account

          Account account
          if message is read request, it only contains accountNo. if message is update request, it contains accountNo and the updated version of account object. if message is insert request, it contains accountNo and initial fields of account object. if message is withdrawal or deposit, it only contains accountNo. if message is transfer request, it only contains accountNo of the source.

        • financialAmount

          java.lang.Double financialAmount
          in financial requests (withdrawal, deposit, transfer) shows the amount of money. in other kinds of request is null.

        • financialAccountNo2

          java.lang.String financialAccountNo2
          in transfer requests shows the accountNo of the destination account. in other kinds of request is null.

    • Class com.mobilab.accountservice.bussiness.message.MyResponse extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -1685169833836386596L

      • Serialized Fields

        • responseType

          short responseType

        • id

          long id
          message id , assigned by gate. each response id is same as its request id.

        • gateID

          java.lang.Long gateID
          id of the gate process.

        • sender

          java.lang.String sender
          end user id, IP or name

        • timestamp

          long timestamp
          time when request arrived

        • status

          short status
          status of response, for example STATUS_DATABASE_ERROR

        • error

          java.lang.String error
          if an exception occur, is its message

        • account

          Account account
          for read request is search result. for update request is updated account for create request is created account for withdrawal / deposit / transfer requests contains only new balance
